"{\"uid\": \"aljazeera.com-sports-2024-8-11-sifan-hassan-puts-on-a-fight-to-win-marathon-gold-at-paris-olympics-2024\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Once an Ethiopian asylum seeker, the Dutch distance running great won her third medal of the Paris Olympics in a thrilling finish to the women's marathon.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 154, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8, \"end\": 17, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9291305010844811, \"rank\": 0.07627507455937872, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}, {\"begin\": 37, \"end\": 42, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9997830390269741, \"rank\": 0.00021695657412856427, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Save  Share  Sifan Hassan completed her mission impossible with a gruelling women's marathon win on the sun-baked streets of Paris on the last day of the Olympics, giving the games a dramatic ending of her own.\", \"from\": 156, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 169, \"end\": 181, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sifan Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\"}, {\"begin\": 281, \"end\": 286, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With the final track and field medal of the games up for grabs on Sunday and with sporting powerhouses grappling for dominance, it was the once-Ethiopian refugee in the Netherlands who gave the Olympics a thrilling sprint finish to bag her third medal in Paris.\", \"from\": 368, \"to\": 629, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 537, \"end\": 548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999996553015, \"rank\": 3.4456945827515834e-10, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 623, \"end\": 628, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan had taken on what many considered to be a crazy gamble, competing in the 5,000m, the 10,000m and the marathon - the last two events just two days apart.\", \"from\": 631, \"to\": 790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 631, \"end\": 637, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in a scintillating sprint finish, Hassan overhauled Ethiopia's Tigst Assefa to take gold by three seconds in an Olympic record of 2hr 22min 55sec.\", \"from\": 792, \"to\": 942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 830, \"end\": 836, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 848, \"end\": 856, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"score\": 0.9999999961605681, \"rank\": 3.4723903425390054e-09, \"text\": \"Ethiopia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Assefa took silver in 2:22.58 and Kenya's Hellen Obiri claimed bronze in 2:23.10.\", \"from\": 943, \"to\": 1024, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 977, \"end\": 982, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.9999999314386537, \"rank\": 6.852946367779166e-08, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 985, \"end\": 997, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellen_Obiri\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Hellen Obiri\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellen_Obiri\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hellen_Obiri\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Friday, Hassan had taken bronze in the 10,000m in the Stade de France after coming away with a bronze in the 5,000m.\", \"from\": 1026, \"to\": 1145, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1037, \"end\": 1043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She fell to the ground on the blue carpet in front of the golden dome of Les Invalides memorial complex in the heart of Paris before grabbing a Dutch flag to celebrate an extraordinary achievement.\", \"from\": 1147, \"to\": 1344, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1220, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0260586275051984e-31, \"text\": \"Les Invalides\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Les_Invalides\"}, {\"begin\": 1267, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1291, \"end\": 1301, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch flag\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Flag_of_the_Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was not easy,\\\" said Hassan, 31.\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1381, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1370, \"end\": 1376, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was so hot, but I was feeling OK.\", \"from\": 1382, \"to\": 1419, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I have never pushed myself through to the finish line as I did today.\\\"\", \"from\": 1420, \"to\": 1490, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Every moment in the race I was regretting that I ran the 5,000m and 10,000m.\", \"from\": 1492, \"to\": 1569, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was telling myself if I had not done that, I would feel great today.\", \"from\": 1570, \"to\": 1640, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"From the beginning to the end, it was so hard.\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1689, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Every step of the way.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1712, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I was thinking, 'Why did I do that?\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1748, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"What is wrong with me?'\", \"from\": 1749, \"to\": 1772, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Back home at Eindhoven Atletiek, an athletics club in the Netherlands, young hopefuls are put through their paces, dreaming of emulating their most famous member - double Olympic champion Sifan Hassan.\", \"from\": 1776, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1789, \"end\": 1798, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 1.1831096497468748e-10, \"text\": \"Eindhoven\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\"}, {\"begin\": 1834, \"end\": 1845, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999996553015, \"rank\": 3.4456945827515834e-10, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}, {\"begin\": 1964, \"end\": 1976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sifan Hassan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sifan_Hassan\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"More than a decade ago, Hassan - a young asylum seeker from Ethiopia - embarked on a journey that would lead to history at the Tokyo Olympics with two golds and a marathon championship in Paris.\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2173, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2003, \"end\": 2009, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 2167, \"end\": 2172, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We immediately saw she was a talented athlete.\", \"from\": 2175, \"to\": 2222, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Even a blind horse could see she would be a good runner,\\\" said Ad Peeters, president of the Eindhoven Atletiek coaching team.\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2315, \"end\": 2324, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 1.1831096497468748e-10, \"text\": \"Eindhoven\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Hassan's first appearance came about as pure chance and in slightly farcical circumstances, explained Peeters, also a middle-distance runner who competed with her in the early days.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2354, \"end\": 2360, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan tagged along with a friend representing the club at a 1,000-metre race nearby - and decided to join in.\", \"from\": 2537, \"to\": 2647, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2537, \"end\": 2543, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But 1,000 metres is two and a half laps of the track.\", \"from\": 2649, \"to\": 2703, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They had not realised that, so they actually tried to finish at the starting line,\\\" laughed Peeters, 58.\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2808, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"So that's how we got to know her.\", \"from\": 2810, \"to\": 2844, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We could already see she was a talented athlete at that time, but she wasn't really a runner then yet,\\\" he told AFP.\", \"from\": 2845, \"to\": 2961, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2957, \"end\": 2960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"score\": 0.9999999999954525, \"rank\": 4.616871711908788e-12, \"text\": \"AFP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Agence_France-Presse\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of Hassan's favourite mottos, taken from the Quran, is \\\"with hardship will be ease\\\", and her formative years were anything but easy.\", \"from\": 2963, \"to\": 3099, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2970, \"end\": 2976, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 3012, \"end\": 3017, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.2209453633116197e-26, \"text\": \"Quran\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Quran\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Born in Adama, southeast of the Ethiopian capital Addis Ababa, Hassan was raised on a farm by her mother and grandmother.\", \"from\": 3101, \"to\": 3222, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3109, \"end\": 3114, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adama\", \"score\": 0.9999984774351782, \"rank\": 1.5225670118346918e-06, \"text\": \"Adama\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adama\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adama\"}, {\"begin\": 3133, \"end\": 3142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9291305010844811, \"rank\": 0.07627507455937872, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}, {\"begin\": 3151, \"end\": 3162, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addis_Ababa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.181266369099418e-20, \"text\": \"Addis Ababa\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addis_Ababa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Addis_Ababa\"}, {\"begin\": 3164, \"end\": 3170, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Aged 15, she left for the Netherlands.\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3261, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3249, \"end\": 3260, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999996553015, \"rank\": 3.4456945827515834e-10, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has never explained why.\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3290, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was first housed in a centre for underaged asylum seekers in Zuidlaren, in the northern Netherlands.\", \"from\": 3292, \"to\": 3396, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3357, \"end\": 3366, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zuidlaren\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Zuidlaren\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zuidlaren\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Zuidlaren\"}, {\"begin\": 3384, \"end\": 3395, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9999999996553015, \"rank\": 3.4456945827515834e-10, \"text\": \"Netherlands\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She told De Volkskrant daily that she cried there every day.\", \"from\": 3397, \"to\": 3457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3406, \"end\": 3419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_Volkskrant\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"De Volkskrant\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_Volkskrant\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/De_Volkskrant\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was like a flower that got no sun,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3459, \"to\": 3507, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She finally arrived in Eindhoven to do a nursing course and fell in with other Ethiopians, some of whom were members of the local athletics club.\", \"from\": 3509, \"to\": 3654, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3532, \"end\": 3541, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 1.1831096497468748e-10, \"text\": \"Eindhoven\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\"}, {\"begin\": 3588, \"end\": 3598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9884040985665687, \"rank\": 0.011731943632687166, \"text\": \"Ethiopians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She took some time to \\\"de-ice\\\", as Peeters puts it, describing her as a \\\"shy girl\\\" in the shadow of some of the more established Ethiopian runners.\", \"from\": 3656, \"to\": 3803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3785, \"end\": 3794, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"score\": 0.9291305010844811, \"rank\": 0.07627507455937872, \"text\": \"Ethiopian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ethiopians\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan herself has recalled training so hard \\\"that my leg was bleeding\\\", but Peeters tells a slightly different story.\", \"from\": 3805, \"to\": 3923, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3805, \"end\": 3811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I actually do not think she was lazy, but it was not always easy to get her to training on time,\\\" he remembered with a chuckle.\", \"from\": 3925, \"to\": 4053, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She did not yet have the discipline to do the training.\", \"from\": 4055, \"to\": 4111, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But I also do not want to underestimate what it's like to be here as a youngster, as a 17-year-old girl, to be lonely, uncertain about your future,\\\" said Peeters.\", \"from\": 4112, \"to\": 4274, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The club worked on her technique.\", \"from\": 4276, \"to\": 4309, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was clearly a \\\"natural\\\" runner, but \\\"her legs and arms were going everywhere\\\" said the coach.\", \"from\": 4310, \"to\": 4407, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Peeters feels the club's main role in Hassan's success came as much off the track as on it - helping her navigate life as a solo teenage asylum seeker.\", \"from\": 4409, \"to\": 4560, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4447, \"end\": 4453, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We made sure she did not do the wrong things, neither in training, nor in her personal life.\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4655, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We kept her safe, picked her up by car to go to training, took her to competitions,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4656, \"to\": 4749, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We kept her in one piece, basically.\\\"\", \"from\": 4751, \"to\": 4789, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Progress came quickly, as did a Dutch passport.\", \"from\": 4791, \"to\": 4838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4823, \"end\": 4837, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_passport\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dutch passport\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_passport\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_passport\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Dutch athletics coaches recognised her talent and sent her to the elite Olympic training centre in Papendal.\", \"from\": 4839, \"to\": 4951, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4843, \"end\": 4848, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"score\": 0.9997830390269741, \"rank\": 0.00021695657412856427, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Netherlands\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The rest is history: at the delayed Tokyo Olympics in 2021, Hassan became the first athlete ever to win medals (two gold, one bronze) in the 1,500m, 5,000m, and 10,000m.\", \"from\": 4953, \"to\": 5122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5013, \"end\": 5019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In Paris, she attempted the even more arduous combination of 5,000m, 10,000m and the marathon.\", \"from\": 5124, \"to\": 5218, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5127, \"end\": 5132, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Despite Hassan's success, her Eindhoven links have stayed strong, said Peeters.\", \"from\": 5220, \"to\": 5299, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5228, \"end\": 5234, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 5250, \"end\": 5259, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"score\": 0.999999999875854, \"rank\": 1.1831096497468748e-10, \"text\": \"Eindhoven\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Eindhoven_Marathon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The club helped her financially at the start of her career and she would often return for training.\", \"from\": 5300, \"to\": 5399, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Hassan remains a club member despite now living and training in the United States, and Peeters collects her fan mail.\", \"from\": 5401, \"to\": 5518, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5401, \"end\": 5407, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"score\": 0.9999392698238502, \"rank\": 5.501696924139231e-05, \"text\": \"Hassan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hasan_ibn_Ali\"}, {\"begin\": 5469, \"end\": 5482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9977966713084712, \"rank\": 0.0021791271966617896, \"text\": \"United States\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nothing stops the training, he said, while admitting that the club would gather round the bar to cheer on their famous alumna in Paris.\", \"from\": 5520, \"to\": 5655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5649, \"end\": 5654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999995453, \"rank\": 2.427571081160374e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We do not stop our training for football, but we do for Sifan.\\\"\", \"from\": 5657, \"to\": 5721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 5741, \"to\": 5767, \"entities\": []}]}"